ul Bass<\/strong> on the importance of beauty:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;I want everything we do to be beautiful. I don&#8217;t give a damn whether the client understands that that&#8217;s worth anything, or that the client thinks it&#8217;s worth anything, or whether it is worth anything. It&#8217;s worth it to me. It&#8217;s the way I want to live my life. I want to make beautiful things, even if nobody cares.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=tfDCNpaPBiA\">\u200b<em>On Making Money vs Quality Work<\/em>\u200b<\/a><em><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you often silently complaining about in your head and who is the person you need to actually discuss your frustrations with?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>People can&#8217;t react to your thoughts, only your actions. Time spent complaining to yourself is often better spent selling someone else on a new way of doing things.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br><a href=\"http:\/\/jamesclear.com\/atomic-habits\">\u200b<em>Atomic Habits<\/em><\/a><em>, the #1 best-selling book<br>\u200b<a href=\"https:\/\/apps.apple.com\/us\/app\/atoms-from-atomic-habits\/id6474421906\">Atoms<\/a>, the official Atomic Habits app<br>\u200b<a href=\"http:\/\/jamesclear.com\/3-2-1\">3-2-1 newsletter<\/a>&nbsp;with 3 million subscribers<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>p.s.<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/Screenshot-2024-05-30-at-1.52.05-PM.png\">\u00a0I think I would be friends with this man\u200b.<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;It&#8217;s never the right time, but right now is usually the best time.&#8221; \u200bII. &#8220;A simple rule that makes life easier: Always strive t